data.title: 1872) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Was the great grandson of Atahobia (Yowani Choctaw) listed on the Treaty of Doak's Stand and Sally McCoy (Half-blood Chickasaw) listed on the 1818 Chickasaw Annuity Roll.  Was with Piety Jane Posey (Muscogee-Creek Indian) abt 1845. No known children from this union.   Married Julia Ann Marie Collins (non-Indian) on May...
